	<internal-name>Intro</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-top</sectionClass_s>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Trick or treat!&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Wait, you expected us to give you sweeties?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Sorry reader, this is Velocity Club, not your gogo&amp;rsquo;s house. Here we are very grown-up. We are only interested in important life issues and super serious financial advice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Now, go trick or treat someone else&amp;rsquo;s blog, please. We&amp;rsquo;ve got to get back inside. We just got &amp;lsquo;Frozen 2&amp;rsquo; in and that box of finger biscuits is not going to eat itself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Just kidding. Back to business!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Today&amp;rsquo;s blog is Halloween themed because we can and because the financial world is full of trickery. Velocity Club is here to give you some yummy financial treats to help you avoid those unpredictable tricks out there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;We begin with that old favourite of ours: Credit cards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Credit cards&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trick: Paying using a credit card every time we don&amp;rsquo;t have the cash.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are all in the habit of doing this, let&amp;rsquo;s be honest. But trickery is afoot.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
