	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #ffbe00; color: #323232 !important;"&gt;The credit card company will candy-coat your debt by telling you that all you need to pay is the minimum payment and all is well.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
