	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-top</sectionClass_s>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p class="fw-900 no-margin-bottom" style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--body-line-height); font-weight: 900; color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Treat: Open a savings account and save towards emergencies instead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="no-margin-top" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); margin-top: 0px; color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;We recommend opening a cheap savings account to put money away for your own emergency fund. Most banks offer low cost or even no cost savings accounts if you have an existing transactional (cheque or credit card) account with them, so look into this for an affordable savings account.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;This special savings account can become a sort of &amp;lsquo;self insurance&amp;rsquo; against life&amp;rsquo;s unexpected events so that you don&amp;rsquo;t have to turn to credit at those times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;How much should you save?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Ideally, you should aim to have 3 to 6 months&amp;rsquo; worth of expenses saved in your account. That sounds like a lot though, so start with whatever you can afford and build on it every month from there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Just like in the movie Frozen, the financial world is full of trickery trying to upset your way of life and turn you into a princess with the ability to freeze your surroundings on a whim.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Actually, hang on, that&amp;rsquo;s a different script.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Let me have a look here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Ah! Here it is: Financial trickery can cost you more than the cost of overpaying on your tax bill or using credit too often and if you aren&amp;rsquo;t careful, you can end up poorer for it. In today&amp;rsquo;s blog, we&amp;rsquo;ve given you some easy, practical things you can do today to protect your income and your credit. You can pay off your credit card debt at the end of each month. You can find legal methods to reduce your tax burden, and you can create a savings account to help pay for unexpected emergency expenses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;If you still have questions and need assistance planning your taxes, your credit repayments or setting up your emergency fund, our highly trained Velocity Club financial advisers are here to support you. They&amp;rsquo;ll help you make the right decisions, every time, to ensure that you reach your financial goals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent; color: var(--color-black);" data-tf-slider="Sgz7HGMv" data-tf-width="550" data-tf-hidden="utm_source=CTA,utm_medium=website,utm_campaign=velocityclub_site,utm_term=,utm_content=" data-tf-loaded="true"&gt;Contact us&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;today; we&amp;rsquo;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
